        <svcsubproc>
            <title>Brake Switch Operation</title>
            <para>The service brake circuit signals the ECM when the brakes are applied. The information is used to
                disengage the Cruise control and Power Takeoff (PTO) function. The brake signal will interrupt the Cold
                Ambient Protection (CAP) feature and will reset the time interval for the Idle Shutdown Timer (IST)
                feature.
            </para>
        </svcsubproc>
